Rating: 4
AWESOME recipe. This sauce has a very earthy flavor, especially when the meat is smoked. The sauce works very well for pork as well, and can be prepared for casual or more formal dining. I first used this recipe for catering events, and it never failed to get raving comments from diners. This is a keeper and terrific for a night when something 'a little different' is in order. YUM.

